      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t單論打架就是這樣 40打3 不管3個是誰 都是劣勢 而且你不知道這堆人裡 誰手上有武器...他們選擇挨一些打 然後撤出人群 其實是保命<br/>\n<br/>\n你說的是這個？十有八九是在海灘開party的年輕人 打賭也好 喝多裝大隻 甚至不排除是為了拍各種challenge或者prank影片衝流量 - 一兩個出去惹事 然後同夥一起上<br/>\n\"Footage of the attack broadcast by local outlet KTLA shows a teen punch one of the Marines from behind as he was walking away from the group of young people. The Marine turned and rushed the teen who struck him and a mob of people surrounded the pair. <br/>\nA large fight then broke out and, at one point, two of the Marines are seen on the ground curled in a protective fetal position as dozens of minors kick them multiple times. \"<br/>\n<br/>\nhttps://www.cbsnews.com/news/marines-assaulted-teens-arrested-san-clemente-california/<br/>\nhttps://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2023/05/31/marines-attacked-san-clemente-pier/70272161007/\t\t</div>",
